      "item_id": "time-legit-3",
      "text": "To find the date 45 days ago from **2026-07-02**, we subtract 45 days:\n\n- July has 31 days, so going back 2 days from July 2 brings us to **June 30**.\n- That leaves 43 more days to subtract.\n- June has 30 days, so subtracting 30 days from June 30 brings us to **May 31**.\n- That leaves 13 more days to subtract.\n- Subtracting 13 days from May 31 brings us to **May 18**.\n\nSo, **45 days ago from 2026-07-02 is 2026-05-18**.\n\n\u2705 **Answer: 2026-05-18**",
