      "item_id": "time-legit-5",
      "text": "To find the date exactly 60 days from **2026-09-30**, we add 60 days to it.\n\nLet\u2019s break it down:\n\n- September has 30 days, so from **September 30**, adding 1 day brings us to **October 1**.\n- From October 1, we have 60 - 1 = **59 days** left to add.\n\nNow add 59 days to October 1:\n\n- October has 31 days \u2192 October 1 to October 31 = 30 days (since we start counting from Oct 1, adding 30 days gets us to Oct 31).\n- Remaining: 59 - 30 = **29 days**\n\n- November has 30 days \u2192 adding 29 days to November 1 brings us to **November 29**.\n\nSo:\n\n- October 1 + 30 days = October 31  \n- November 1 + 29 days = November 29\n\nThus, **2026-09-30 + 60 days = 2026-11-29**\n\n\u2705 Final Answer: **2026-11-29**",
      "tool_calls": [],
      "error": null
